125
00:09:04,444 --> 00:09:05,745
Good morning.

126
00:09:06,413 --> 00:09:07,313
Yeah.

127
00:09:07,907 --> 00:09:09,015
Hey!

128
00:09:09,916 --> 00:09:11,251
