Yeah...

150
00:11:24,047 --> 00:11:25,051
Akira-kun,

151
00:11:25,864 --> 00:11:27,520
are you okay?

152
00:11:28,333 --> 00:11:29,122
Yes,

153
00:11:29,770 --> 00:11:30,890
