228
00:16:19,545 --> 00:16:21,569
That's a suspicious look on your face.

229
00:16:21,741 --> 00:16:22,915
Tell me!

230
00:16:30,680 --> 00:16:32,391
Hey, Shu-san, wait!

231
00:16:33,594 --> 00:16:35,561
