234
00:16:39,741 --> 00:16:41,133
Shu-kun, thanks for your hard work.

235
00:16:42,268 --> 00:16:44,170
I came today to talk to Shin.

236
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:45,471
Me?

237
00:16:45,650 --> 00:16:46,439
Yeah.

238
00:16:46,556 --> 00:16:48,341
I heard from Sakurako-chan.

239
00:16:49,141 --> 00:16:50,009
Why

240
00:16:50,415 --> 00:16:52,111
