241
00:16:52,376 --> 00:16:53,312
Huh?

242
00:16:53,570 --> 00:16:55,781
Why did you leave Akira-san's place?

243
00:16:56,266 --> 00:16:57,049
Well,

244
00:16:57,729 --> 00:16:59,775
my parents' house finished renovations,

245
00:16:59,807 --> 00:17:00,286
so I...

246
00:17:00,310 --> 00:17:01,420
That's not it!

247
00:17:01,475 --> 00:17:03,623
- You and Akira-san...
- Asuka.

248
00:17:03,904 --> 00:17:05,091
Shu-kun.

249
00:17:06,578 --> 00:17:07,493
But...

250
00:17:07,775 --> 00:17:09,529
Let's go.

251
00:17:10,904 --> 00:17:12,298
Wait, Shu-kun.

252
00:17:16,526 --> 00:17:17,803
