254
00:17:19,358 --> 00:17:20,306
But...

255
00:17:20,478 --> 00:17:22,478
It's Akira-kun's decision.

256
00:17:26,081 --> 00:17:27,480
Shu-kun,

257
00:17:28,742 --> 00:17:30,049
what if, let's say,

258
00:17:30,074 --> 00:17:31,754
I forgot about you...

259
00:17:34,320 --> 00:17:35,288
