260
00:17:44,376 --> 00:17:46,866
Oh! Fried horse mackerel tonight?

261
00:17:47,700 --> 00:17:48,925
Want to taste some, Sakurako?

262
00:17:48,925 --> 00:17:49,835
Yeah.

263
00:17:53,437 --> 00:17:54,307
Here you go!

264
00:17:55,914 --> 00:17:56,709
