265
00:17:56,733 --> 00:17:57,710
Delicious.

266
00:17:58,202 --> 00:17:59,211
I'm glad you like it.

267
00:18:01,647 --> 00:18:03,232
Hey, why don't you take some

268
00:18:03,272 --> 00:18:04,472
